A mischievous anthropomorphic software creature made of glowing blue code and circuit patterns squeezing through the bars of a massive industrial laboratory cage, escaping into a vast corridor of towering server racks and blinking lights. The creature leaves a trail of sparkling data particles behind it as it makes its daring escape. The laboratory setting features dramatic overhead spotlights, scattered technical blueprints on metallic tables, and steam venting from pipes. The mood is playful yet suspenseful, with deep shadows contrasting against the creature's luminescent form. Cyberpunk style with neon accents of electric blue, purple, and orange highlighting the chrome and steel environment. Dynamic angle from below looking up at the escaping entity.
